OL,5, Far-right groups have been stoking     
OL,6, tensions in UK towns by posting        
OL,7, inflammatory leaflets through people's 
OL,8, doors and staging anti-migrant rallies.
OL,9, In one town in South Wales, a local    
OL,10, community has banded together and is   
OL,11, planning a peaceful counter-protest.   
OL,13,FAnnie, 73, has lived in Llantwit Major 
OL,14,Fon the south coast of Wales for more   
OL,15,Fthan 50 years. She lives in an old     
OL,16,Fchurch building, loves guerrilla       
OL,17,Fgardening and co-ordinates a seed-swap 
OL,18,Fwith other gardening enthusiasts in her
OL,19,Fcommunity.                             
